11#include "media/base/h264_profile_level_id.h"
12
13// TODO(crbug.com/1187565): Remove this file once downstream projects stop
14// depend on it.
15
16namespace webrtc {
17namespace H264 {
18
19absl::optional<ProfileLevelId> ParseProfileLevelId(const char* str) {
20 return webrtc::ParseH264ProfileLevelId(str);
21}
22
23absl::optional<ProfileLevelId> ParseSdpProfileLevelId(
24 const SdpVideoFormat::Parameters& params) {
25 return webrtc::ParseSdpForH264ProfileLevelId(params);
26}
27
28absl::optional<Level> SupportedLevel(int max_frame_pixel_count, float max_fps) {
29 return webrtc::H264SupportedLevel(max_frame_pixel_count, max_fps);
30}
31
32absl::optional<std::string> ProfileLevelIdToString(
33 const ProfileLevelId& profile_level_id) {
34 return webrtc::H264ProfileLevelIdToString(profile_level_id);
35}
36
37bool IsSameH264Profile(const SdpVideoFormat::Parameters& params1,
38 const SdpVideoFormat::Parameters& params2) {
39 return webrtc::H264IsSameProfile(params1, params2);
40}
41
42} // namespace H264
43} // namespace webrtc
